    <HeaderContainer>
      <Header>My Work:</Header>

      <StyledWork>
        <ProjectCard name="Tenners" source="https://res.cloudinary.com/fsuffieldcode/image/upload/v1584036305/tenners.jpg" />
        <ProjectCard name="The Irish Times" source="https://res.cloudinary.com/fsuffieldcode/image/upload/v1584036919/theirishtimes.jpg" />
        <ProjectCard name="Tenners" source="https://res.cloudinary.com/fsuffieldcode/image/upload/v1584036305/tenners.jpg" />
      </StyledWork>

  )
}

export default Work
